    "(8)As demonstrated in Table VIII, we utilize the standard errors of {Metric IF } to represent instruction sensitivity.",
    "To varying degrees, it is observed across all evaluated models, which poses a potential challenge to the models' fundamental perception and cognition capabilities.",
    "The results indicate that Qwen2.5-Omni-7B exhibits relatively high instruction sensitivity, with its Instruction-Following Rate (IFR) showing sharp declines in certain tasks.",
